<p>Try to find the answer of the following questions by yourself
<br>
<div align="justify">
		<ol><li>What is the pH value of water?	</li>	
		<li> Which indicator will you choose to detect the titration point of a weak acid and a strong base? 
	</li>
	<li>Do you know any acid-base indicator(s) that can be used for a weak acid-strong base as well as strong acid-weak base pair titrations?</li>
	<li>Name some naturally occurring acid-base indicators.</li>
	<li>What will you use for precise measurement of pH: acid-base indicators, pH test papers or a pH meter?</li>	
	</ol></p>
